  <name>Next Meeting for COSMIC</name>
  <summary>Show your next calendar event in the COSMIC panel</summary>
  <description>
    <p>A beautiful panel applet for the COSMIC desktop that displays your next upcoming calendar event right in your panel.</p>
    <p>Features include one-click join for video calls (Google Meet, Zoom, Teams, Webex), calendar color indicators, flexible time display, and smart filtering options.</p>
    <p>Uses Evolution Data Server (EDS) to read user calendars. This needs to be configured separately.</p>
  </description>
